Package: GoogleScholarScrapeR
Type: Package
Title: Scrape Google Scholar for an Author's Publications
Version: 0.1
Date: 2015-07-06
Author: Susan VanderPlas
Maintainer: Susan VanderPlas <srvanderplas+googlescholarscraper@gmail.com>
Description: Searches google scholar for an author and (possibly) institution, and downloads the bibtex citations and other information into a table.
License: CrapL
LazyData: TRUE
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Imports: httr, rvest, digest, magrittr, stringr, xml2
Suggests: knitr, roxygen2